		"excerpt": "Ubuntu us are doing the round trip! It’s time to live - WAN you arrive at GHC, come meet us and say HELO (we love GNU faces, we’ll be very api to meet you). When you’re exhausted like IPv4, git over to the Cloudflare corner to reboot.",
		"feature_image": "https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/tJvpeD54efn8CNRWOSNrH/a32e60ebc48c439580bc5fdf5577cfbe/ghc.png",
		"featured": false,
		"html": "<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ubuntu_(operating_system)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ubuntu</a> us are doing the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Round-trip_delay_time\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">round trip</a>! It’s <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_to_live\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">time to live</a> - <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wide_area_network\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WAN</a> you arrive at GHC, come meet us and say <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simple_Mail_Transfer_Protocol\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">HELO</a> (we love <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GNU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GNU</a> faces, we’ll be very <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Application_programming_interface\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">api</a> to meet you). When you’re exhausted like <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IPv4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IPv4</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Git\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">git</a> over to the Cloudflare corner to reboot –– we’ll have chargers and Wi-Fi (it’s not a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transmission_Control_Protocol#CONNECTION-ESTABLISHMENT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SYN</a> to <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Representational_state_transfer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">REST</a>). <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/R_(programming_language)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">R</a> booth can be your <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esc_key\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ESC</a>. Then Thursday morning <a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/e/grace-hopper-better-together-breakfast-sponsored-by-cloudflare-zendesk-tickets-38404240116\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">we’re hosting a breakfast</a> <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bash_(Unix_shell)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">bash</a> with Zendesk –– it will be quite the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Assembly_language\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Assembly</a>, you should definitely <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Go_(programming_language)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Go</a>,<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Compiler\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">compile</a> a bowl of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Serial_communication\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">serial</a>, drink a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">bit</a> of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Classless_Inter-Domain_Routing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CIDR</a> or a cup of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tee_(command)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">tee</a>.</p><p>I’m also speaking at 1:30PM on Wednesday in OCCC W414 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cryptographic_hash_function\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hashing</a> out encryption and updates for IoT –– <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Data_Encryption_Standard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">DES</a> should be a fun <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Session_(computer_science)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">session</a>.</p><p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transmission_Control_Protocol\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ACK!</a> I did <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Network_address_translation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">NAT</a> tell you how to find us. <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Checksum\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Check for sum</a> women in capes a few <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hop_(networking)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hops away</a> from the booths with the lava <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LAMP_(software_bundle)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LAMP</a> stack. I&#39;m the one with <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CURL\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">cURLs</a>.</p><p>In <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/D_(programming_language)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">D</a> air! Excited to <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Local_area_network\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LAN</a>d. <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/C_(programming_language)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">C</a> you soon.</p>\n            <figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card \">\n            \n            <Image src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/1tjItgsesKtLjcPjox0PI0/231114e3a4bc152a74ecc2b9f77a0534/gradient-Corgi.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kg-image\" width=\"1600\" height=\"805\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n            \n            </figure>",
